page.title: 03Ecology (Cont)
page.content:
MAMMALS
Rabbit, brown hare, hedgehog, fox, harvest mouse, house mouse, dormouse, common shrew, water shrew, mole, brown rat, warter vole, bank vole, pipistrell bat, weasel, stoat.
BIRDS
Hedge sparrow, house sparrow, tree sparrow, mistle thrush, song thrush, starling, black bird, magpie, chaffinch, sky lark, robin, bull finch, blue tit, great tit, yellow hammer, swift, swallow, house martin, wood pigeon, carrion crow, rook, jackdaw, kestral, cuckoo, wren, tawny owl, barn owl, pheasant, partridge, lapwing, stock dove (collared), coot, moorhen, mallard, swan, black headed gull, herring gull, gold finch.
